{"data":[{"date":"07:11 22/08","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 22/8 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/lich-thi-dau-asiad-2018-ngay-hom-nay-228-cua-doan-ttvn.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h xin g\u1eedi t\u1edbi qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e1c m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao \u1edf ASIAD 2018 di\u1ec5n ra trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 22/8 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c V\u0110V thu\u1ed9c \u0111o\u00e0n Th\u1ec3 thao Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u0110o\u00e0n th\u1ec3 thao Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tranh t\u00e0i nhi\u1ec1u m\u00f4n trong ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 4 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. T\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m ng\u00e0y tranh t\u00e0i h\u00f4m nay c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 l\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o m\u00f4n xe \u0111\u1ea1p.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u1ede \u0111\u1ea5y, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tranh t\u00e0i \u1edf n\u1ed9i dung 100km \u0111ua \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u1eef l\u00fac 10h00 s\u00e1ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 n\u1ed9i dung th\u1ebf m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 t\u1eebng gi\u00fap Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, xe \u0111\u1ea1p \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u01b0\u1eddng x\u1ea3y ra nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd kh\u00f3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111ua, v\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 hy v\u1ecdng Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y may m\u1eafn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc HCV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho \u0111o\u00e0n th\u1ec3 thao Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asian Games 2018.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNgo\u00e0i Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u00f4n thi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. \u1ede m\u00f4n wushu, Ho\u00e0ng Th\u1ecb Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng Giang thi chung k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1eddng quy\u1ec1n n\u1eef l\u00fac 10h. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nT\u1edbi bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i, Nghi\u00eam V\u0103n \u00dd thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft t\u00e1n th\u1ee7 h\u1ea1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 60 kg v\u1edbi v\u00f5 s\u0129 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Trung Qu\u1ed1c Wang Xuetao. C\u00f9ng gi\u1edd, B\u00f9i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng Giang \u0111\u1ea5u Kumar Santosh Kumar (\u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9) \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft t\u00e1n th\u1ee7 nam h\u1ea1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 56 kg.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u1ede m\u00f4n b\u1eafn s\u00fang, ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u 22/8 l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c x\u1ea1 th\u1ee7 n\u1eef. Ph\u1ea1m Th\u1ecb H\u00e0 v\u00e0 L\u00ea Th\u1ecb Linh Chi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i s\u00fang ng\u1eafn 25 m, trong khi Nguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n Trang v\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Ng\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i s\u00fang tr\u01b0\u1eddng 3 t\u01b0 th\u1ebf. C\u1ea3 2 n\u1ed9i dung c\u00f9ng b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00fac 9h.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nC\u00e1c V\u0110V c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i TDDC s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft n\u1ed9i dung \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c ph\u1ea7n thi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. \u0110\u1ed9i TDDC nam b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00fac 14h, 4 ti\u1ebfng sau t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ed9i n\u1eef.<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 228 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 228 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/Lich-thi-dau-Asiad-2018-ngay-hom-nay-228-cua-doan-TTVN-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 228 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 228 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/ltdasiad2.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\