; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Man City mua Jasper Cillessen c\u1ee7a Barca v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, Man xanh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m Jasper Cillessen</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Man City nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au khi Claudio Bravo d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi 6 th\u00e1ng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u00e2u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa n\u1ebfu ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a anh di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City mua Jasper Cillessen v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Man City mua Jasper Cillessen v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Man-City-mua-Jasper-Cillessen-vao-thang-1-nam-2019-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City nh\u1eafm Cillessen thay Bravo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMan City v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 Ederson, song h\u1ecd c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u00ean r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7. Theo Daily Mail, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1eefa v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJasper Cillessen l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Man City. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf Camp Nou, anh c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCillessen \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Italia quan t\u00e2m, song anh v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn. N\u1ebfu Man City t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Man City ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mua Cillessen</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Man City mua Jasper Cillessen c\u1ee7a Barca v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, Man xanh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jasper Cillessen\" title=\"Jasper Cillessen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/7/HLV-Valverde-muon-Cillessen-o-lai-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mua Jasper Cillessen</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh mua th\u00eam th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh mua Jasper Cillessen c\u1ee7a Barca.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Man City \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m Jasper Cillessen, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man xanh v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/hlv-valverde-muon-cillessen-o-lai-barca-180-193784.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Valverde mu\u1ed1n Cillessen \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca</span>. Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng d\u00e0nh cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 Marc-Andre ter Stegen.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 Valverde mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Cillessen \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u01b0ng \u00fd, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2633","checkdouble":"195024"},{"date":"08:30 22/08","title":"B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi danh t\u00ednh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/bat-ngo-voi-danh-tinh-cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-mua-giai-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Gary Neville v\u00e0 Jamie Carragher s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n Premier League 2018/19, bao g\u1ed3m danh t\u00ednh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, top 4, vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd n\u1eb1m \u1edf s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i khi gi\u1ed1ng nhau \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0nh, c\u1ea3 hai c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Man Utd v\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn David Silva. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng Mohamed Salah, Harry Kane hay b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Big Six, \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee9 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Manchester City.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gary Neville v\u00e0 Jamie Carragher d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Premier League 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gary Neville v\u00e0 Jamie Carragher d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Premier League 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/bat-ngo-voi-danh-tinh-cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-mua-giai-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gary Neville v\u00e0 Jamie Carragher d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 Neville v\u00e0 Carragher c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch l\u1ea5y l\u00f2ng c\u00e1c C\u0110V Man City khi c\u00f2n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad s\u1ebd b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 Liverpool. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola c\u0169ng \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng Premier League 2018/19 sau hai v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">S\u1ef1 tr\u00f9ng h\u1ee3p th\u00fa v\u1ecb gi\u1eefa hai huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u00f2n \u1edf c\u1ea3 danh s\u00e1ch th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh top 4, bao g\u1ed3m Liverpool v\u00e0 Manchester United c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Tottenham, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i chi\u1ebfu v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t su\u00f4t t\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal thay t\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u01b0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1eadn khi s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3i qua n\u0103m th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1eadt b\u00e3i tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 Champions League. Neville v\u00e0 Carragher c\u0169ng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Everton s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0 chen ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m 6 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">S\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn \u1edf nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n kh\u00e1c, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng xem nh\u1ea5t (Neville &ndash; Alisson Becker v\u00e0 Carragher &ndash; Naby Keita) c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t (Phil Foden c\u1ee7a Man City v\u00e0 Ryan Sessegnon c\u1ee7a Fulham).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 nh\u1ea5t, Neville v\u00e0 Carragher chia r\u1ebd quan \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 danh hi\u1ec7u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Mohamed Salah m\u00e0 thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0 Sergio Aguero v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0 Harry Kane.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2632","checkdouble":"195025"},{"date":"08:26 22/08","title":"H\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/hang-loat-doi-bong-lon-nhan-don-dau-vu-pjanic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Miralem Pjanic gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2023, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u ch\u1ea5m h\u1ebft cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn trong vi\u1ec7c nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Miralem Pjanic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Miralem Pjanic c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus t\u1eeb Roma v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2016 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 32 tri\u1ec7u euro, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin. 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Juventus.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Miralem Pjanic gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Miralem Pjanic gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/hang-loat-doi-bong-lon-nhan-don-dau-vu-pjanic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn mu\u1ed1n mua Pjanic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i Pjanic ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn 44 l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990 r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng khi v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng l\u1ea1i v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Pjanic l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A v\u00e0 C\u00fap QG Italia v\u1edbi Juventus trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-tinh-chi-60-trieu-euro-mua-pjanic-180-194470.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Miralem Pjanic</span>, Chelsea v\u00e0 Man City c\u0169ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990. Khi m\u00e0 phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u00ec Los Blancos \u0111ang m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t ng\u1ef1a trong vi\u1ec7c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Pjanic.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN nh\u1eafm Miralem Pjanic thay Luka Modric, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i. Real ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 70 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Juventus nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au v\u1ee5 Miralem Pjanic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Miralem Pjanic gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2023, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u ch\u1ea5m h\u1ebft cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn trong vi\u1ec7c nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus vs Porto Pjanic\" title=\"Juventus vs Porto Pjanic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/2/23/juventus-tu-choi-ban-sao-khung-cho-man-city-voi-gia-50-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Pjanic gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00eda Juventus x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i, anh s\u1ebd g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 6 n\u0103m 2023. \u0110\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Pjanic h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Juventus v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Juventus, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Miralem Pjanic l\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd y\u00ean t\u00e2m c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2631","checkdouble":"195028"},{"date":"08:36 22/08","title":"Man City ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mua sao Barca v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/4/man-city-phu-nhan-mua-cillessen-vao-thang-1.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Man City mua Jasper Cillessen c\u1ee7a Barca v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, Man xanh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m Jasper Cillessen</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Man City nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au khi Claudio Bravo d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi 6 th\u00e1ng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u00e2u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa n\u1ebfu ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a anh di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City mua Jasper Cillessen v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Man City mua Jasper Cillessen v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Man-City-mua-Jasper-Cillessen-vao-thang-1-nam-2019-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City nh\u1eafm Cillessen thay Bravo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMan City v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 Ederson, song h\u1ecd c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u00ean r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7. Theo Daily Mail, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1eefa v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJasper Cillessen l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Man City. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf Camp Nou, anh c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCillessen \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Italia quan t\u00e2m, song anh v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn. N\u1ebfu Man City t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Man City ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mua Cillessen</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Man City mua Jasper Cillessen c\u1ee7a Barca v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, Man xanh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jasper Cillessen\" title=\"Jasper Cillessen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/7/HLV-Valverde-muon-Cillessen-o-lai-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mua Jasper Cillessen</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh mua th\u00eam th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh mua Jasper Cillessen c\u1ee7a Barca.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Man City \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m Jasper Cillessen, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man xanh v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/hlv-valverde-muon-cillessen-o-lai-barca-180-193784.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Valverde mu\u1ed1n Cillessen \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca</span>. Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng d\u00e0nh cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 Marc-Andre ter Stegen.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 Valverde mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Cillessen \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u01b0ng \u00fd, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2630","checkdouble":"195029"},{"date":"08:37 22/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Blackburn vs Reading 01h45 ng\u00e0y 23/8 (H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/nhan-dinh-blackburn-vs-reading-01h45-ngay-238-hang-nhat-anh-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay Blackburn vs Reading 01h45 ng\u00e0y 23/8 (V\u00f2ng 4 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh Championship 2018/19): \u00dd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Blackburn vs Reading 01h45 ng\u00e0y 238 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Blackburn vs Reading 01h45 ng\u00e0y 238 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/Blackburn-vs-Reading.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Blackburn vs Reading</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Blackburn vs Reading: 2-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y Reading l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 nh\u1eb1n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Blackburn. 5 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t hai \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf Championship, \"Hoa h\u1ed3ng\" ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n n\u00e0y, Blackburn l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh sau 1 m\u00f9a chinh chi\u1ebfn \u1edf League One. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng Blackburn Rovers kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 3 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i (th\u1eafng 1, h\u00f2a 2). Tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, Reading \u0111\u00e3 to\u00e0n thua c\u1ea3 3 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. T\u00ednh c\u1ea3 lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Paul Clement \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ea1ch 9 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Reading c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t khi ch\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 20 tr\u00ean BXH, h\u01a1n \u0111\u00fang 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m so v\u1edbi nh\u00f3m xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng. M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Reading l\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch. Theo \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Paul Clement \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf 6/7 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u1edf 3 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Blackburn ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng, trong khi con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y b\u00ean ph\u00eda Reading l\u00e0 1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Reading ch\u1ec9 thua 1/5 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Blackburn Rovers g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (th\u1eafng 1, h\u00f2a 1, thua 3).<br>\r\n- C\u1ea3 3 m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n- Blackburn Rovers ch\u1ec9 thua 1/6 cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Reading tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y (th\u1eafng 3, h\u00f2a 2, thua 1).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN L\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br>\r\n- Blackburn: V\u1eafng Ben Gladwin v\u00e0 Jacob Davenport (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng); Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Derrick Williams c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf.<br>\r\n- Reading: V\u1eafng David Edwards, Garath McCleary, Callum Harriott, Jordan Obita, Chris Gunter v\u00e0 Sone Aluko (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng).</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2629","checkdouble":"195032"},{"date":"08:57 22/08","title":"\u0110\u1ec3 t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169, Real ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u201ctr\u00ean tr\u1eddi\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/real-phai-tra-120-trieu-euro-de-mua-rodrigo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 120 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua Rodrigo. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u00e0 Valencia \u0111\u1eb7t ra cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft Rodrigo</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u b\u01b0\u1edbc th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Rodrigo Moreno. Anh ghi t\u1edbi 19 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, bao g\u1ed3m 16 t\u1ea1i La Liga, gi\u00fap Valencia gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQua \u0111\u00f3, Rodrigo \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. C\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecfa l\u1ef1c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 27 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 120 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua Rodrigo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 120 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua Rodrigo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/real-phai-tra-120-trieu-euro-de-mua-rodrigo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Real ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 120 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua Rodrigo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Rodrigo t\u1eebng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Real m\u00f9a 2009/2010. Anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng l\u1ea1 g\u00ec HLV Julen Lopetegui khi t\u1eebng h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c tr\u00ean U21 v\u00e0 \u0110TQG T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ph\u1ea3i mua v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Mateu Alemany c\u1ee7a Valencia \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng Real ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 120 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua Rodrigo. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00fang \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Real Madrid\u201d, Alemany n\u00f3i v\u1edbi BeIN SPORT khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u201cN\u1ebfu h\u1ecd b\u1ecf ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 120 tri\u1ec7u Euro, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec kh\u00e1c.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng Rodrigo c\u00f3 v\u1ebb r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a La Liga m\u00f9a m\u1edbi 2018/19, Valencia \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a Atletico Madrid 1-1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00ednh Rodrigo l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho \u201cB\u1ea7y d\u01a1i\u201d sau b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Angel Correa ph\u00eda b\u00ean kia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-voi-80-trieu-euro-cho-rodrigo-moi-di-cho-khac-180-192338.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/goc-real-voi-80-trieu-euro-cho-rodrigo-moi-di-cho-khac.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-voi-80-trieu-euro-cho-rodrigo-moi-di-cho-khac-180-192338.html\">G\u00f3c Real: V\u00f2i 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho Rodrigo? M\u1eddi \u0111i ch\u1ed7 kh\u00e1c!</span><br>\r\n<span>Bi\u1ebft Real Madrid \u0111ang kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t m\u0169i c\u00f4ng thay th\u1ebf Cristiano Ronaldo, Valencia \u00e9p gi\u00e1 tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Rodrigo. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-san-sang-nha-nguoi-thua-rafinha-180-194985.html\">Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u1ea3 \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba\u201d Rafinha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-sap-chi-200-trieu-euro-nang-cap-doi-hinh-180-194897.html\">Real Madrid s\u1eafp chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-nang-gia-hoi-mua-cavani-len-63-trieu-bang-180-194880.html\">Real Madrid n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-chinh-thuc-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-madrid-172-194831.html\">Hazard ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-hazard-172-194702.html\">HLV Sarri l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Hazard</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2628","checkdouble":"195036"},{"date":"08:46 22/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m nay 22/8","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/asiad-2018-ngay-hom-nay-228.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 22/8: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn, th\u00f4ng tin, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c V\u0110V thu\u1ed9c \u0111o\u00e0n th\u1ec3 thao Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 22/8.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/bang-tong-sap-huy-chuong-asiad-2018-472-194760.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/bang-tong-sap-huy-chuong-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/bang-tong-sap-huy-chuong-asiad-2018-472-194760.html\">B\u1ea2NG T\u1ed4NG S\u1eaeP HUY CH\u01af\u01a0NG ASIAD 2018</span><br />\r\n<span>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u1ebd c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c B\u1ea3ng t\u1ed5ng s\u1eafp huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng ASIAD 2018, B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng Asiad 2018 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n Th\u1ec3 Thao Vi\u1ec7t Nam di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>TH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH C\u1ee6A TTVN T\u1ea0I ASIAD 2018</h2>\r\n3 HCB<br />\r\n- Th\u1ea1ch Kim Tu\u1ea5n (c\u1eed t\u1ea1, 56kg nam)<br />\r\n- Ph\u1ea1m Qu\u1ed1c Kh\u00e1nh (wushu)<br />\r\n- Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n Vinh (c\u1eed t\u1ea1, 62kg nam)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n4 HC\u0110<br />\r\n- Taekwondo (n\u1ed9i dung quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i nam)<br />\r\n- b\u1eafn s\u00fang (10m s\u00fang ng\u1eafn h\u01a1i h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p nam n\u1eef).<br />\r\n- Nguy\u1ec5n Huy Ho\u00e0ng (b\u01a1i 800m t\u1ef1 do nam)<br />\r\n- D\u01b0\u01a1ng Th\u00fay Vi (wushu)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSau ng\u00e0y 21/8 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, th\u1ec3 thao Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng kh\u00e1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ng\u00e0y 22/8. Nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c1 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Thu\u1eadt s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111ua xe \u0111\u1ea1p \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u1eef l\u00fac 10h s\u00e1ng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nH\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 2, tay \u0111ua ng\u01b0\u1eddi An Giang v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111ua xe \u0111\u1ea1p ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Myanmar. C\u00f4 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh l\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh d\u00e0i 106 km sau 3 gi\u1edd 11 ph\u00fat 59 gi\u00e2y, gi\u00e0nh HCV. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110o\u00e0n th\u1ec3 thao Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m nay.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNgo\u00e0i Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u00f4n thi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. \u1ede m\u00f4n wushu, Ho\u00e0ng Th\u1ecb Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng Giang thi chung k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1eddng quy\u1ec1n n\u1eef l\u00fac 10h.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m nay 228 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m nay 228 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/Truc-tiep-Asiad-2018-ngay-228,-ket-qua-Asiad-2018-hom-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m nay 228 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y thi \u011