n-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay Aston Villa vs Brentford 01h45 ng\u00e0y 23/8 (V\u00f2ng 4 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh Championship 2018/19): \u00dd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Aston Villa vs Brentford 01h45 ng\u00e0y 238 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Aston Villa vs Brentford 01h45 ng\u00e0y 238 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/Aston-Villa-vs-Brentford.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Aston Villa vs Brentford</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span>Aston Villa vs Brentford: 1-2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i Aston Vila \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng Premier League. Trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u00f2ng play-off g\u1eb7p Fulham, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Villa Park \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc 0-1. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e0ng th\u00f4i th\u00fac th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Steve Bruce th\u00eam quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 su\u00f4n s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau 3 v\u00f2ng, Aston Vila th\u1eafng 2, h\u00f2a 1, \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 5 tr\u00ean BXH. Xen k\u1ebd c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Championship, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Yeovil Town 1-0 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 C\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Anh. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, The Villans ca kh\u00fac kh\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n 7/9 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 v\u1eady, nh\u01b0ng Aston Villa b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Brentford c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u00fa \u201c\u0111\u1ec1-pa\u201d r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t khi qu\u1eadt ng\u00e3 Rotherham (5-1), Sheffield Wed (2-0) v\u00e0 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Stoke (1-1) \u1edf 3 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, Brentford \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu chu\u1ed7i 4 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 8/9 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y (th\u1eafng 7).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, n\u00ean m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Brentford.\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 10 tr\u1eadn, Aston Villa th\u1eafng 5, h\u00f2a 3, thua 2.<br>\r\n- Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Aston Villa, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 th\u1eafng 2, h\u00f2a 3, thua 0. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN L\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br>\r\nAston Villa: Keinan Davis, Scott Hogan (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng).<br>\r\nBrentford: Rico Henry, Emiliano Marcondes (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng).\u00a0 </div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2626","checkdouble":"195038"},{"date":"19:47 21/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 21/8: H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/diem-tin-toi-218-ha-duc-chinh-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Mourinho b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t gi\u1ed1ng Wenger,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 21/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb HLV Arsene Wenger, Thierry Henry \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Bourdeaux. Henry t\u1eebng g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng gi\u00fap \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 ba chung cu\u1ed9c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 trong vai tr\u00f2 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 218 H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 218 H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/duc-chinh-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Bahrain t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i, H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 l\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gabriel Jesus t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Sergio Aguero tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n cho Man City t\u1ea1i Premier League.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean Farabi Firdausy c\u1ee7a Indonesia nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Quang H\u1ea3i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ed1c \u0110\u00f4ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng c\u00fa \u0111\u1ec7m l\u00f2ng hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Roberto Firmino \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 Philippe Coutinho. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Firmino \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 36 b\u00e0n, k\u00e9m Coutinho 5 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, Chelsea \u0111ang d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Eden Hazard nh\u1eb1m gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 ve v\u00e3n c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Hazard s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 300.000 b\u1ea3ng m\u1ed7i tu\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u1eadm n\u1eef Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 0-7, HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec1m ch\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 to ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n trong gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1eefa hai hi\u1ec7p. D\u00f9 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng A.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho\" title=\"Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/mu-phan-ung-ra-sao-sau-tin-don-sa-thai-mourinho-bo-nhiem-zidane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Jose Mourinho \u0111ang trong t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1ea1i Man Utd.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Arsenal, Ian Wright nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t Jose Mourinho \u0111ang c\u00f3 chung ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh v\u1edbi Arsene Wenger trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m cu\u1ed1i, khi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u m\u1ea5t l\u00f2ng tin nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng t\u1eeb c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 t\u1eeb Transfermarkt, Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb cao g\u1ea5p 16 l\u1ea7n so v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam (2.03 tri\u1ec7u so v\u1edbi 125.000 euro). D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i trong khi Th\u00e1i Lan b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vincent Kompany kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 Man City kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ef1 m\u00e3n sau ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League 2017-18. Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 Man City l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 10 n\u0103m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn ng\u00e0y 21/8:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-dai-dien-cua-pogba-chi-trich-huyen-thoai-mu-172-195008.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Pogba ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-sap-mua-duoc-gavin-bazunu-172-195006.html\">Man City chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tu\u1ed5i teen</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/marc-cucurella-muon-roi-barca-180-195005.html\">T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Barca quy\u1ebft d\u1ee9t \u00e1o ra \u0111i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-2108-180-195004.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 21/08</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-quoc-len-tieng-canh-bao-olympic-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195003.html\">B\u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-dau-palace-02-liverpool-172-195001.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Palace 0-2 Liverpool</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2625","checkdouble":"195009"},{"date":"19:55 21/08","title":"B\u1ecb gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/bi-gioi-chuyen-mon-chi-trich-sau-tran-gap-nhat-ban-hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n chi\u1ec1u 21/8, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft khi H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng b\u1ecb g\u00e3y ng\u00f3n ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u, trong khi Quang H\u1ea3i c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eb9.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ecb gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u1ecb gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-thanh-cong-cung-dt-olympic-viet-nam.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV&nbsp;Park Hang Seo ph\u1ea3n b\u00e1c nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;&ldquo;Gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch v\u00e0 ph\u00ea ph\u00e1n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. V\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Olympic Nepal, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng sau. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00ec ch\u00fang ta ch\u01b0a x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Nepal, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. T\u1ed1n s\u1ee9c th\u00ec tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o c\u0169ng t\u1ed1n s\u1ee9c th\u00f4i. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n thay \u0111\u1ed5i nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta nh\u1eadn tr\u1eadn thua tan t\u00e1c r\u1ed3i, khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 phi\u1ec1n l\u00f2ng&rdquo;. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Theo \u00f4ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mu\u1ed1nsong kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu, \u00f4ng Park t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i kh\u00e9o: &ldquo;T\u00f4i xin gi\u1eef b\u00ed m\u1eadt v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u Bahrain \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y 23/8 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-218-ha-duc-chinh-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-184-195009.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/diem-tin-toi-218-ha-duc-chinh-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-218-ha-duc-chinh-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-184-195009.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 21/8: H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nH\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Mourinho b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t gi\u1ed1ng Wenger,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 21/8.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-quoc-len-tieng-canh-bao-olympic-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195003.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/bao-han-quoc-len-tieng-canh-bao-olympic-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-quoc-len-tieng-canh-bao-olympic-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195003.html\">B\u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y t\u1edd Chosun (H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c) \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ee7 quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-thai-phan-ung-the-nao-sau-man-trinh-dien-te-hai-cua-doi-nha-o-asiad-168-195000.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/nguoi-thai-phan-ung-the-nao-sau-man-trinh-dien-te-hai-cua-doi-nha-o-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-thai-phan-ung-the-nao-sau-man-trinh-dien-te-hai-cua-doi-nha-o-asiad-168-195000.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng th\u1ebf n\u00e0o sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u1edf ASIAD?</span><br>\r\nGi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Ch\u00f9a v\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ea1i ASIAD v\u1eeba qua, trong khi L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 suy...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhin-lai-nhung-tran-thua-cua-bong-da-bahrain-truoc-viet-nam-168-194992.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/10/26/Khep-lai-VCK-U19-chau-A-2016-Buoc-ngoat-lich-su-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhin-lai-nhung-tran-thua-cua-bong-da-bahrain-truoc-viet-nam-168-194992.html\">Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Bahrain tr\u01b0\u1edbc Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Bahrain. V\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111ang nghi\u00eang h\u1eb3n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2624","checkdouble":"195010"},{"date":"20:10 21/08","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/thu-mon-bui-tien-dung-lap-ky-luc-tai-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o s\u00e2u khi c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Man Utd, Lee Sharpe ch\u00ea Paul Pogba th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 k\u00e9m \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn t\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ed3i s\u1ee5t c\u1ee7a \"qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\".</h2><h2>C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Man Utd ch\u00ea Paul Pogba<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi Paul Scholes l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man Utd thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean, \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1ed9t c\u1ef1u \"qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\" kh\u00e1c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng. Lee Sharpe b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Scholes khi cho r\u1eb1ng Pogba thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Man Utd.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Man Utd ch\u00ea Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Man Utd ch\u00ea Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Cuu-danh-thu-Man-Utd-che-Paul-Pogba-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Man Utd ch\u00ea Paul Pogba kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Anh \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n\" - C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Man Utd ch\u00ea Paul Pogba: \"Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5y ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n c\u1ee7a anh \u1ea5y trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, ch\u00e0ng trai cao l\u1edbn n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft anh \u1ea5t n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 d\u1eabn t\u1eeb hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn anh \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00fang kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng. L\u1ebd ra, Pogba ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng minh anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong m\u1ecdi tu\u1ea7n. Nh\u01b0ng v\u00ec m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i l\u00fd do, Pogba kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\".\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i v\u1ec1 Pogba<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a Man Utd v\u1edbi Brighton (2-3) t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018-19, Scholes \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ra c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Pogba. Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau, Mino Raiola - ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Pogba - \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Scholes.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Paul Pogba \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018. M\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 chi\u00eau tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Mino Raiola nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u00f2i ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Man Utd t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cho Pogba.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-dai-dien-cua-pogba-chi-trich-huyen-thoai-mu-172-195008.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Pogba ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sieu-co-raiola-chi-trich-scholes-san-sang-dem-pogba-roi-mu-172-194987.html\">Si\u00eau c\u00f2 Raiola ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Scholes, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111em Pogba r\u1eddi M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-218-barca-dinh-ngay-don-pogba-184-194949.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 21/8: Barca \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3n Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/scholes-chi-trich-pogba-sau-tran-thua-brighton-172-194879.html\">Scholes \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 l\u1eddi nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pogba-len-tieng-xin-loi-sau-tran-thua-bac-nhuoc-cua-mu-172-194851.html\">Pogba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng xin l\u1ed7i sau tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pogba-va-mourinho-can-phai-truong-thanh-hon-172-194812.html\">Pogba v\u00e0 Mourinho c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2623","checkdouble":"195011"},{"date":"20:26 21/08","title":"N\u00f3ng: Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf V-League v\u00ec l\u00fd do b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/14/nong-nam-dinh-san-sang-bo-vleague-vi-ly-do-bat-ngo.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1eeb l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1ec9nh, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf V-League \u0111\u1ec3 quay tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t.</h2><h2>Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf V-League<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n tr\u00ean OnSports, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi chia s\u1ebb \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ee9c x\u00fac r\u1eb1ng d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1ec9nh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC: &quot;Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n khi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m&quot;.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u00f3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf V-League v\u00ec l\u00fd do b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"N\u00f3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf V-League v\u00ec l\u00fd do b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/nong-nam-dinh-san-sang-bo-vleague-vi-ly-do-bat-ngo.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf V-League \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n&quot;Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u01b0 ki\u1ec3u mu\u1ed1n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quay tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu th\u1ea3 h\u1eb3n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf th\u00ec c\u1ee9 n\u00f3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nu\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau b\u1ea3y n\u0103m v\u1eafng b\u00f3ng, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i V-League \u1edf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 18 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 20 v\u00f2ng, \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u00e1p ch\u00f3t khi ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111\u00fang 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>V\u00ec \u0111\u00e2u n\u00ean n\u1ed7i<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i V-League 2018 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a quen v\u1edbi nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eeb HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, ngo\u1ea1i binh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1ed9t l\u00fd do kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu kinh ph\u00ed ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u1eabn s\u1ed1ng nh\u1edd b\u1ea7u s\u1eefa c\u1ee7a t\u1ec9nh n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n l\u1ef1c t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf V-League. N\u1ebfu t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec thay \u0111\u1ed5i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng 21 V-League 2018, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br />\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC t\u1ea1i V-League 2018:</h2>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/danh-roi-chien-thang-truoc-clb-ha-noi-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi-168-191331.html\">\u0110\u00e1nh r\u01a1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HLV Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/cdv-nam-dinh-doi-mua-dot-phao-ngay-tai-hang-day-291-191271.html\">C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i m\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng ngay t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/ha-noi-vs-nam-dinh-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191252.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 3-3 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh (KT): D\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3-0, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/clb-nam-dinh-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-sau-vu-nao-loan-tren-san-thien-truong-168-190948.html\">CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t sau v\u1ee5 n\u00e1o lo\u1ea1n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cdv-nam-dinh-dai-nao-san-thien-truong-nguoi-trong-cuoc-noi-gi-168-190610.html\">C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea1i n\u00e1o s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/de-thua-tuong-moi-cua-sai-gon-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi-168-190140.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 thua t\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, HLV Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2622","checkdouble":"195012"},{"date":"20:18 21/08","title":"ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u00ean nh\u1eefng k\u00eanh n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/asiad-2018-se-duoc-phat-song-tren-nhung-kenh-nao-tai-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u00ean truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 xem l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay tr\u00ean k\u00eanh VTC1, VTC3, VTC9 c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0i Truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1 VTC v\u00e0 k\u00eanh VOVTV.</h2><p style=\"text-align: left;\">T\u1eeb ng\u00e0y mai (22/8) kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem ASIAD 2018 c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n tr\u00ean c\u00e1c k\u00eanh s\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1 VTC tr\u1ef1c thu\u1ed9c \u0110\u00e0i ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i Vi\u1ec7t Nam VOV. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, tr\u00ean ph\u00e1t thanh, th\u00ednh gi\u1ea3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nghe t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Qu\u1ed1c gia, \u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Olympic v\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n n\u1eef qu\u1ed1c gia Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 thao kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Asiad 2018 tr\u00ean c\u00e1c k\u00eanh s\u00f3ng ph\u00e1t thanh: VOV1, VOV2, VOV3, VOV Giao th\u00f4ng, VOV S\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/ban-quyen-asiad-2018-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ASIAD 2018 tr\u00ean k\u00eanh VTC1, VTC3, VTC9 c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0i Truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1 VTC v\u00e0 k\u00eanh VOV TV V\u1eady ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng k\u00eanh n\u00e0y \u1edf nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh  n\u00e0o. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u00e1c k\u00eanh n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t trong nh\u00f3m k\u00eanh mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0i VTC tr\u00ean h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng  truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed DVB-T2. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ecba b\u00e0n n\u1eb1m trong v\u00f9ng ph\u1ee7 s\u00f3ng truy\u1ec1n  h\u00ecnh s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a VTC s\u1ebd thu xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed k\u00eanh n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ec3 thu xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n s\u1eed  d\u1ee5ng tivi c\u00f3 t\u00edch h\u1ee3p DVB-T2, ho\u1eb7c tivi \u0111\u1eddi c\u0169 th\u00ec c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7u thu truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh s\u1ed1  m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t (DVB-T2 v\u00e0 DVB-T) \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh  \u0111\u1eb9p ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i s\u00f3ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a VTC \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 \u1edf c\u00e1c t\u1ec9nh \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1eb1ng B\u1eafc B\u1ed9, Nam B\u1ed9,  m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u1ec9nh mi\u1ec1n n\u00fai nh\u01b0 Cao B\u1eb1ng, S\u01a1n La, \u1edf T\u00e2y Nguy\u00ean c\u00f3 \u0110\u1eafc L\u1eafc c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ee7  s\u00f3ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh s\u1ed1 DVB-T2 \u1edf \u0111\u1ecba b\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra tr\u00ean c\u00e1c h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n, ch\u1ec9 tr\u1eeb K+ l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e1t c\u00e1c k\u00eanh c\u1ee7a VTC c\u00f2n  l\u1ea1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n nh\u01b0 VTVcab, SCTV, FPT, Viettel,  MyTV, HTVC, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh s\u1ed1 v\u1ec7 tinh VTC \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 truy\u1ec1n d\u1eabn k\u00eanh VTC3, VTC1 ho\u1eb7c VTC9. Do  \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n (tr\u1eeb  K+) \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c n\u1ed9i dung ASIAD. Tuy nhi\u00ean ri\u00eang k\u00eanh VOV TV th\u00ec c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, VTC c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea5p quy\u1ec1n cho c\u00e1c \u0110\u00e0i ph\u00e1t thanh - Truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh trong c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc, n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 nhu c\u1ea7u, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ti\u1ebfp ph\u00e1t nguy\u00ean tr\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh, c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u do VOV/VTC ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 ASIAD 2018. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0110\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Vi\u1ec7t Nam (VTV) cho hay \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi VTC v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng nguy\u00ean v\u1eb9n ASIAD 2018 tr\u00ean c\u00e1c k\u00eanh qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 c\u1ee7a VTV.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean v\u00e0i k\u00eanh qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a VTV nh\u01b0 VTV3, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ebd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 xem ASIAD 2018 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p, c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng truy\u1ec1n d\u1eabn s\u1ebd gi\u00fap  ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u1ecfi ph\u1ea3i l\u00f9ng s\u1ee5c \u0111i t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng \u201cl\u1eadu\u201d \u0111\u1ec3 xem nh\u01b0  10 ng\u00e0y qua.</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2621","checkdouble":"195013"}]}